tripleo_ansible/roles/tripleo_ceph_clien.message:
In Standalone, for example, storage_ip is not defined within the inventory, so I guess we can improve this task with something like:
ctlplane is always used [1] if storage is not there
````
    - name: Get ceph_mon_ip addresses
      set_fact:
        tripleo_ceph_client_mon_ips: |
           {%- set mons = [] %}
           {%- set net = 'storage_ip' %}
           {%- for host in groups['ceph_mon'] %}
             {%- if hostvars[host]['storage_ip'] is not defined %}
               {%- set net = 'ctlplane_ip' %}
             {%- endif %}
           {%- set _ = mons.append(hostvars[host][net]) %}
           {%- endfor %}
           {{ mons  }}
      when:
        - (tripleo_enabled_services | intersect(['ceph_mon'])) and
          (groups['ceph_mon'] | length > 0)
```

[1] https://github.com/openstack/tripleo-heat-templates/blob/master/network/service_net_map.j2.yaml#L74-L78

